    drm/radeon: add a dpm quirk for all R7 370 parts
    
    Higher mclk values are not stable due to a bug somewhere.
    Limit them for now.
    
    Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
    Cc: stable@vger.kernel.org

